                     <interp inst="t18320906-325-person2679" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I received him in charge with the cloak.</p>
               <p>MRS. BEARD. This is our cloak - I saw the prisoner's<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183209060136"></xptr>hand come through the hole, and called my husband to go out.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in the booth at the time she hallooed out that she had lost her cloak - a parcel of people were round the booth at the time, making a noise about a bad half-crown; he came, and gave charge of me.</p>
